**NEWSLETTER TELLMATIC**

The tellmatic newsletter script developed by Volker Augustin has been around for some time, sadly the author is no longer actively developing it. I needed to update my relatively old (but working) version to work with PHP 5.5 and looked around for a replacement. Sadly most of the scripts out there to purchase are very badly written, after trying a couple I decided to stick with Tellmatic - better the devil you know...

I have forked the latest version (1.0.9-rc2) and will attempt to fix the bugs that I find and enhance it where possible.

Please note, I do not intend to infringe on any intellectual ownership or possible copyright issues with this software. I simply want to continue using a newsletter system that in my opinion is still one of the best free scripts around. For simple newsletter delivery it does what it should do, and still does it well.

Many thanks to Volker Augustin for the time and effort he as invested in this Newsletter system.


